'''Tamaceqt''' d tutlayt [[tutlayin titergiyin|tatergit]]. Ttmesmlayen-tt ttwareg n Lmali (ladɣa deg temnaḍt n [[Timbuktu]]). Tesɛa snat n tintalyin : ''Timbuktu'' (Tanaslamt) akked ''Tadɣaq'' (Kidal), deg [[Mali]]. 

Tamaceqt n [[Burkina Faso]] tettcabi aṭas i Tamaceqt  n lmali.<ref>[http://www.mondeberbere.com/langue/tamasheq/ David Sudlow, 2001, ''The Tamasheq of Nord-East Burkina Faso: Notes on grammar and syntax including a key vocabulary'', Köln, Rüdiger Köppe Verlag]</ref>

Tikkal, isem Tamaceqt/Tamaceq yettuseqdac deg wemkan tutalyin titergiyin.

